 2020-03082020-05-10,  ,  ,  FIN, 
ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectCanada Enterprise Emergency Funding Corporation
PrecisOrder declaring that subsections 89(1), (4), and (6) and section 89.1 of the FINANCIAL ADMINISTRATION ACT, that apply only to parent Crown corporations, apply to CANADA ENTERPRISE EMERGENCY FUNDING CORPORATION as if it were a parent Crown corporation, effective on the day on which Canada Enterprise Emergency Funding Corporation is incorporated.
